column6: Parma77 Fashion Light Green Jade Queen Bangle Bracelet Christmas Gift
column13: Even more stunning than the picture
column14:
This light green jade bracelet from Parma77 is more stunning than the picture on the product page.

The bracelet arrives in a lovely, satin lined presentation box. The bracelet is is then inside a gorgeous, lined brocade drawstring pouch. Parma77 put a lot of thought in packaging this so that it would make a spectacular gift for someone special - or for yourself!

I have very large hands so I ordered the large size. I can get it on but I really think it's because I have flexible and limber hands. I think the large size would fit a woman with average sized hands very well so keep that in mind when ordering.

This bangle bracelet is a beautiful, light green, slightly translucent jade. I'm no gemologist but this definitely seems to be natural jade. It's weighty and feels very cool to the touch. It's beautifully finished and polished. As shown in the picture, it's flat inside and the surface is curved on the outside. (Parma77 also makes some natural stone bracelets that are round - curved on the inside and outside.)

It looks so elegant on my wrist and because of the simple classic style, it goes with anything. I can dress up or dress casually and it's appropriate for either. I'm so enamored of it, I think I will order some of the other colors Parma77 offers this bracelet in.

Jade has been considered lucky for centuries and is thought to bring the wearer luck, health, protection from enemies and love. Because of this, it's considered to be a special gift. I don't know if that's true, but I do know this would make a fabulous gift.

NOTE: I received a free or discounted sample for review but a positive review was not asked for, promised or implied.

They are exquisite, plus got great service 2015-08-10 US 25410223 RIDVIN108HULH B00FF7VJ7G 333098381 14K White Gold Solitaire Diamond Engagement Ring Round Brilliant Cut ( J Color VS2 Clarity 3.8 ctw) Jewelry 3 7 8 N N READ THIS FIRST - BUY ONLY GIA CERTIFIED DO NOT BUY FROM THESE PEOPLE!
I purchased an emerald diamond ring for my proposal, it arrived just in time, I proposed and she said yes!!
That is the good news. I then took the ring to a jeweler and gemologist to be checked out.
The ring was sold to me as a VS2 clarity, very good cut, E color. Turns out it is more like an I-1 clarity with inclusions visible to the naked eye, the cut is poor, and the color is more like a J!!!
This means the ring is worth about half of what it was sold to me as, and it nothing like described. Nice gift for my new fiance to go along with our beautiful new relationship huh!!!
I have contacted the seller twice so far with no response. DO NOT BUY FROM THESE PEOPLE, IT IS LIKELY THAT THEY THINK THEY CAN GET AWAY WITH GIVING POOR QUALITY DIAMONDS BECAUSE MOST PEOPLE WILL NOT CHECK AND THEY WILL JUST GIVE THE RUN AROUND WHEN YOU RESPOND.
I will update hear if I hear anything and get any resolution, UNTIL THEN ASSUME THIS IS A SCAM COMPANY.

08/10/15: UPDATE: finally got a response, they said they could have my ring certified (which it is supposed to be already) or could potentially replace the ring. I will let you know when I get a response as to their replacement offer, and what happens during the process.

08/25/15: UPDATE: After weeks of back and forth, I finally received a replacement ring that is GIA certified, VS1, E color, and the quality that was specified. I paid more for this ring but HDD made a concerted effort to compensate my emotional distress, and provide me with a good product at cost (at least that is what they stated.) I have had the ring inspected, and it is as stated, so ultimately I ended up with a great priced ring, but went through weeks of distress, frustration, paying for inspections, paying for shipping, constant emails etc.
This appears to be a legitimate company with legitimate products at a great price - BUT BEWARE, UNLESS IT IS GIA CERTIFIED, IT IS LIKELY APPRAISED AT A QUALITY MUCH HIGHER THAN IT ACTUALLY IS. column6: 14k White Gold Princess-cut Diamond Bridal Wedding Band Ring (1/2 cttw, H-I, I1-I2)
column14:
I purchase (and, and after seeing the poor quality of the diamonds in many rings of this type, have returned) a lot of rings from Amazon but this one is truly a keeper! Being a 1/2 cttw ring each of the 10 stones are a nice size at 5 points each and being princess cut, they fill the entire top of the ring without any gaps (which you don't get with round cut stones). There is an abundance of sparkle and the width of the ten stones perfectly stretches the entire width of the finger. The width of the band is a very acceptable width compared to some others I have seen that are so thin and fragile. And the price is quite nice as well!

All in all, a beautiful ring that adds a lot of sparkle to my existing rings. Like the vast majority of the previous reviewers, I would definitely recommend the purchase of this ring.

column6: Silicone Wedding Ring by HonorGear, Premium Medical Grade Wedding-Bands for Active Men, Athletes, Comfortable Fit & Skin Safe, Non-toxic, Antibacterial
column13: Silicone bands are versatile and changeable.
column14: This ring is pretty versatile and would be great for a man in between sizes as he could order small and it have a little stretch.  I also thought this would be good for men who can't wear a metal or other hard style ring at work, because this is not that way, it is a softer and more giving ring that molds to the hand.  One small drawback my husband noticed was it was not as smooth as his metal band so it did "catch" on fabric.  It is a rubbery silicone material and that is normal for that, also in washing his hands the moisture was a little more prone to hide under that ring, but those are small things one can get used to, they are minor and not affecting of the style or usefulness of the ring.  I also thing these are good low cost style change alternatives, and good slip on slip off for those who need to for whatever reason, we got grey so that we could use it as a neutral color, and he wore it fow a few days until his other band was fixed.  I would purchase these again, however I was given this ring at a promotional price for my honest review of the item.  They are a low cost alternative.

column13: Unbelievable. This makes me hate Jewelers.
column14:
This ring is freaking awesome. As someone who is not a fan of paying $300+ for the same ring at a retailer because it was made by "Triton", this ring is perfect. It has signifigant weight to it, and looks just as authentic as it feels...because it is. I lift or workout everyday, and this thing doesn't have a scratch on it. I've had many compliments on it's contrast of matte/glossy tones that really look great. Dirt or items will get stuck in the center crease every now and then, but comes out easily. Now if someone can explain to me why identical rings are 20x more I'd love to hear it. But for now, I am 100% satisfied with my purchase. Thank you King Will for an awesome affordable product that doesn't stress me out to get scratched or lose.

Note: In the image it reads "Tungsten" inside the ring. This is false, It actually reads "Tungsten Carbide" and is not engraved. But, for $15, who cares? I will upload a picture when I get a chance.

column6: 18k Gold and Rhodium Plated Sterling Silver Two Tone Diamond Hoop Earrings (1/10cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)
column14:
I absolutely love these heavy, high quality sparkly braided hoop style pierced earrings! The front of the earring facing out on each side has rows of tiny diamonds (1/10 total carat) set in gold and rhodium plated sterling silver creating a very elegant look -- and it will be obvious for you to put the earring in the ear lobe so that the stones face the front so those can be seen. The back of the hoop is plain gold color. The clasp is hinged and is pushed into a grip that locks it into place so you don't have to worry about the earring falling out and the locking pin is thick enough that you won't be concerned that it will break off or bend.

I was quite happy that I was able to ear these for the entire day into evening without any hypersensitivity or irritation that I often can get from a cheap pair of earrings. They really are beautiful and come in a nice gift box perfect for presentation to a special someone if you want to give the set as a present. I love them!

column6: TRUSUPER Jewelry Knitted Mens Multi-Layer Leather Handmade Fashion Bracelet Bangles,Black,Silver
column14:
I don't know what you see when you look at this picture but let me tell you, the piece is probably 100x nicer in person. I think it looks great in the picture but more of cheap piece of jewelry. But when I got it I was very surprised. This bracelet is beautiful., It's a very nice looking material that is also very strong. The bracelet is not flimsy or bendy at all. The beads give it just enough class to make it a dressy or casual piece depending on your mood. The beads are a matte metal but have a slight shine to them. The detail on the center piece is beautiful.
My husband loves it and it fit his wrist perfectly. I think ALL bracelets should have a magnetic clasp because it so easy to put on alone. I can't tell you how many times I fight with a bracelet then give up because I can't get the clasp latched. This one is a very nice magnetic pull the two sides grabs each other within a few inches. And the force is perfect so they stay together and don't work their way open.
The entire bracelet seems very durable so I think it could be worn by a man in any working conditions without falling apart. I'm sure eventually my husband will test my theory so if something happens, I'll update this review.
I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest opinion but the opinion expressed is all my own.

column6: Myia Passiello \Timeless\" Swarovski Zirconia 1 Carat Each Princess Cut Gold Clad Stud Earrings"
column14:
I purchased two pair of these as potential gifts as the price had been greatly discounted. I've bought Myia Passiello jewelry in the past and have been very pleased with the quality. These do not disappoint.

They came individually wrapped in tissue paper, inside a small plastic bag, inside of the attractive and padded presentation box. The stones are clear and sparkly and the gold plated metal is sturdy and lovely. All of the four earrings were intact and lovely and I'm thrilled with them! I hope the recipient will be as well. They are a nice sized stone that looks believably like it could be a diamond, in my opinion.

I would rate them 5 stars but will not until I know how they wear and their durability. I have no qualms about recommending them though, as Myia Passiello jewelry has been a reliable purchase in the past.

column6: Trusuper Fashion Jewellery Stainless Steel Dagger Knife Chain Pendant Necklace,Silver
column14:
My husband fell in love with this necklace the minute he took it out of the pack. He put it on immediately exclaiming how nice it is. I was so happy to see that because he is NOT easy to please at all. I finally got a chance to look at it and I agree the quality is awesome. The pendant is a nice size but is not over sized. It has a nice weight to it and the silver is very pretty. The chain itself is really nice with thicker links and a big lobster claw clasp. I LOVE lobster claws because I know my chain is not going anywhere when I wear it.
Being stainless steel I know we won't have to worry about it rusting no matter what my husband does while he is wearing it. You know working men tend to get dirty, wet, and sweaty and this is necklace/pendant that could be worn under all of those conditions plus more. And it will still look good at the end of the day, even year. The detail put into the knife is amazing. It looks extremely real. There is an amazing shine to the entire piece. This set would make an amazing gift for any man in your life .
I would advise to be careful when handling the knife because in one of my not so finest moments tried to bend it and see how sturdy it is an I popped the blade off. I felt so bad and I have never seem my husband so upset over a piece of jewelry so I just ordered him another one.
I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest opinion but the opinion expressed is all my own.

column13: Beautiful Heart of the Ocean Necklace. *Reminds me of the Titanic necklace*!
column14:
This Heart of the Ocean Necklace by Swarovski Elements is absolutely stunning.
It reminds me of the necklace off my favorite movie "Titanic".

It comes in a nice gift box that you can store it in or give it as a gift.

It has 3 layers of real 18K white gold vacuum plating that is non allergenic.
The chain is 18.50 inches with a 1.99 inch extension if you want to make it longer.
The heart is about 1.45 inches and is beautiful.

This necklace is breathtaking. I wore it last night to dinner and received so many compliments. I love how shiny it is and it didn't fade or turn colors at all. The heart pendant crystal is sparkly and clear, no cloudiness at all. There are crystals (that looks like diamonds) wrapped around the heart in 3 lines and is attached on very strong with a strong plating holding them together in the back.

The pendant also slides off the chain very easily so your able to remove it and put it on a longer chain if you want.

column6: Platinum-Plated 925 Sterling Silver and AAA Cubic Zirconia Bridal Set
column13: A Perfect Stand In..../not so much
column14: I received this set last week. It is lovely. The stones have fire and their sizes are believable. The setting is what was called, back in the day, 'Tiffany' setting. It is tall just like my wedding set. I got this set to be a temporary stand in for my 39 year old set until I can have it resized. Arthritis is not kind to the knuckles sad to say.  My daughter said that she was jealous thinking I had gotten a new diamond wedding set! She was surprised when I told her what it was.  I follow the care of cubic zirconium guidelines available online and so far so good. I will update as time goes on.   Update: exactly 1 month after delivery the mounting broke off while I was reaching into my handbag.  Upon examination, I saw that the soldering point of the mount onto the band of the ring was tiny tiny tiny. No strength or stability there!!  I could not contact Amazon because it was exactly 30 days and they would not accept a return. I wanted to contact them to see if they would do anything about this before I amended my review. There was no option so here is my updated review. DO NOT PURCHASE THIS PRODUCT BECAUSE IT WILL NOT HOLD UP UNDER GENTLE WEARING. FORGET ABOUT IT IF YOU WEAR THINGS ROUGHLY.  DISAPPOINTED IN AMAZON THIS TIME.

column6: 14.75 inch Birdhouse 60 pair Earring Hanger Necklace Bracelet Jewelry Tree Organizer Display Stand
column14:
Oh. My. Gosh. Okay, let me start by saying that I had a couple of concerns when I read the reviews. One specific person said that the little cage didn't come included, another said the bird/leaves were bent or broken off. I received my product with no such issues and it is even prettier than I imagined and highly functional.

There are a couple of CONS that I want to point, in case they matter to you:
1. I wear some larger rings (not even ridiculously gaudy, just larger than a simple band/stone may be) and these do not fit into the little door on the side of the hanging cage. There are two reasons this is not an issue for me: first, the tiny leaves that make up the "roof" of the cage can be gently bent up and create enough room for the ring to go inside without issue, then easily bent back down to cover up again. Might they break off after repeated bending over time? Possible. It doesn't seem like it. Secondly, the little hooks that can be seen on all four corners of the "cage" also hold rings, and I'm fine with placing them there.
2. This thing is actually a little bigger than the shelf I planned to put it on, so make sure you do your measurements before buying. It's beautiful and has just the right amount of distance to keep your necklaces on the top branches from hitting the counter it's sitting on, but, yanno, it's over a foot tall.
3. With the birdcage on one side, you'll want to hang necklaces on the other side to balance the way it looks. That's also the side with the least amount of foot support, so you'll have to distribute your crap evenly. Whatever, it's not a big deal. Just thought you might want to know.

Anyway, all things considered, this thing is *BEAUTIFUL* and highly optimal. I could never even own enough pairs of earrings to fill it up, and it's an excellent product. I guarantee you won't find a better jewelry holder for this price, definitely a worthwhile buy.

column6: MyIDDr - Pre-Engraved & Customized Warfarin Alert Medical Bracelet, Red
column13: Hooks on to EVERYTHING. Extremely annoying and somewhat destructive.
column14:
After wearing this bracelet for over a year, I've decided it is not a very good product. While the materials are durable and have held up, the design is somewhat flawed. There are rings that connect each of the chain pieces to the latches and metal spoon of the actual bracelet. Each of these rings are basic rings with a single notch in them so you can hook them together. The problem is these have a gap in them and grab on to EVERYTHING. I've squished them all together with pliers but they still catch on things. I've ruined 2 work shirts with this bracelet, a $200 comforter for my bed and have hooked the bracelet on numerous other things as well. It's actually quite remarkable how many things these loops manage to grab on to over the course of a year. They even hooked on to my boxers at one point while I was walking. That part isn't a big deal, though it's a bit annoying if you can't get it unhooked on your own.

I've attached 2 photos of my very expensive bed spread to give you an idea of what I'm talking about. No, I do not have cats. ALL of the broken strings and pulled loops are from this medical bracelet. We've only had the bed spread for 6 months and the rest of the spread looks fine with no broken strings or pulled loops. This gives you an idea of just how easy it manages to grab on to things.

My husband said the bracelet is comfortable to wear and does not pinch or pull his arm hair. Which is an extreme plus for any piece of jewelry.
The black ball decorations make the bracelet look much more expensive than the listed price. It's a very dressy bracelet and I see it being a great addition to a man's arm in anything including a tuxedo.

Trusuper Women's Platinum Plated Cubic Zirconia Heart Tennis Bracelet, 7\" Jewelry 4 0 0 N N Very sparkly -- Good for a child I was very excited to review this bracelet. I thought it was adorable when I saw the pictures but when I got it in, it was not my favorite piece of jewelry. It is really shiny which makes it look fake. It's got way too much "bling" for me. I could not see myself wearing this bracelet except for extremely dressy occasions like a wedding but even then I'm thinking it may still be too much.
The details are amazing and each heart is perfectly shaped with a stone in the middle. In the inside of the heart around the stone is beautiful as well but I think all together it's overload.
The clasp is awesome and I love that I can put in on by myself in a few seconds. The is my favorite type clasp for a bracelet for that reason plus it stays on. I have seen this type clasp come open but this one fastens securely so I don't think I have to worry about it falling off. Another great thing is it blends in with the bracelet and it's smooth so it's hardly noticeable. I gave the bracelet to my daughter because she loved it. I think it would make a much better child's bracelet than a women's bracelet.
I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest opinion but the opinion expressed is all my own. 2015-08-10 US 4261539 R31JN6XAM21CE3 B00838E9NU 717884025 Body Candy Howling Wolf Pendant Necklace Jewelry 4 0 0 N Y Think chain. column14:
[[VIDEOID:973c5c1fd8f3aafa3e59acb77485f85e]]I was super excited to get this ring because I broke my engagement ring a few years ago. My husband has offered to buy me a new one, but to be totally honest I haven't wanted to let him spend that kind of money on me again. BUT, I've gotten real tired of the weird looks or nosey questions about why I don't have a ring.

This ring is the perfect solution. I've looked at rings like this in the past but a lot of them seem to really go overboard and look obviously fake. I wanted a ring that looked real enough to stop the questions and not overly gaudy. This ring has done it! I honestly can't stop looking at it. I forgot how much I love wearing my engagement ring and I definitely feel like this has filled a void for me, without causing a big dent in my bank account.

I wear a size 7 ring, so that's what I purchased and it fits great. My left hand has a tendency to swell at night and it's not so tight that I can't get it off if I forget to take it off. Pictures really don't do this ring justice, it is absolutely gorgeous!

I received this product at a discounted rate in exchange for my honest, unbiased review
